	e opens 1 hour prior to door times. You will need a valid photo ID and the
	 credit card used for purchase. ADA tickets can be purchased online - you 
	do not need to call the box office to place an order. Look for the logo on
	 the Find Tickets page to view all available accessible seats. We do have 
