	 have very limited seating available for guests on the day of the event so
	 please make sure you purchase accessible seating when you order tickets. 
	Bags up to 12" x 6" x 12" are allowed in the venue. All bags will be searc
	hed prior to entry. For more FAQs please visit www.houston.houseofblues.co
